content: Is it expected that https://doc.rust-lang.org/nightly/nightly-rustc/rustc_const_eval/interpret/enum.Scalar.html does not list all the inherent methods defined at https://doc.rust-lang.org/nightly/nightly-rustc/src/rustc_middle/mir/interpret/value.rs.html#191 ? seems odd to me...
